    <h3>Here's a time line of Zaha Hadid's designs:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>1993</strong> - The design of Vitra Fire Station, Germany</li>
      <li><strong>2006</strong> - Maggie's Centre, Fife</li>
      <li><strong>2010</strong> - Evelyn Grace Acadamy, London </li>
      <li><strong>2012</strong> - Heydar Aliyev Centre, Baku</li>
      <li><strong>2015</strong> - Messner Mountain Museum, Italy</li>
    </ul>
